Cell["\<\
The section is written in a way that requires bckData/powerData tables only, \
which is also one of the exported quantities. In this way, one can just run \
the simulation at one point, obtain results, and at a different point import \
the data back and just start from there (without running the whole simulation \
again).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987058742982502*^9, 3.987058895633101*^9}, {
  3.987058925840517*^9, 
